20took%20a%20day%20trip%20to%20Monhegan%20Island%20on%20a%20historic%20ferry.%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20took%20a%20historic%20World%20War%20II-era%20ferry%20to%20a%20quaint%20island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Maine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20boat%20was%20bare-bones%2C%20but%20the%20ride%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisit-monhegan-island-in-maine-without-cars-ferry-review-2025-3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMonhegan%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20pleasant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20enjoyed%20a%20full%20day%20on%20the%20scenic%20island%20and%20took%20a%20more%20modern%20ferry%20on%20the%20way%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20join%20my%20best%20friend%20at%20her%20grandparents'%20picture-perfect%20cottage%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaine-state-would-choose-move-to-frequent-traveler-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoast%20of%20Maine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20amble%20lazily%20around%20the%20little%20seaside%20towns%2C%20sunbathe%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20and%20forget%20that%20time%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%2C%20however%2C%20one%20highly%20suggested%20activity%20that%20required%20prior%20planning%3A%20a%20day%20trip%20to%20Monhegan%20Island.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20small%2C%20car-free%20island%20is%20only%20accessible%20by%20boat%2C%20so%20I%20took%20a%20%2453%20round-trip%20ride%20on%20the%20Monhegan%20Boat%20Line%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20took%20the%207%20a.m.%20ride%20on%20a%20historic%20boat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20sitting%20on%20wooden%20benches%20on%20an%20old%20ferry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a174373b4fb977f359805d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20stretch%20our%20day%20trip%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20earliest%20ferry%20available%20at%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20realize%2C%20however%2C%20that%20this%20particular%20time%20slot%20in%20the%20summer%20season%20comes%20with%20a%20special%20treat%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ride%20aboard%20the%20historic%20Laura%20B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%201943%2C%20the%20small%20workboat%20spent%20its%20early%20years%20carrying%20troops%20and%20supplies%20in%20the%20Pacific%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fww2-cold-war-submarine-tour-museums-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorld%20War%20II%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%201946%2C%20it%20started%20running%20lobsters%20from%20Maine%20to%20Boston%20and%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20the%20boat%20is%20stationed%20in%20Port%20Clyde%20and%20carries%20passengers%2C%20mail%2C%20and%20freight%20to%20Monhegan%20Island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ride%20was%20bare-bones%2C%20but%20charming.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Piles%20of%20boxes%20and%20drinks%20on%20the%20front%20of%20a%20boat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a17443f2e5a80cfe04ff683%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tiny%20mailboat's%20wooden%20interior%20is%20no-frills%2C%20with%20four%20rows%20of%20seats%20and%20two%20restrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deck%20was%20filled%20with%20deliveries%20%E2%80%94%20piles%20of%20beverages%20and%20supplies%20for%20the%20island's%20businesses%20sat%20on%20the%20bow%20%E2%80%94%20but%20many%20bright-eyed%20travelers%20opted%20to%20stand%20outside%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20a%2070-minute%20ride%2C%20we%20docked%20at%20Monhegan%20Island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20stand%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20ship%20that's%20pulling%20into%20Monhegan%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1deba5b4fb977f359830f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ride%20to%20Monhegan%20Island%20took%20a%20little%20over%20an%20hour.%20As%20it%20came%20to%20an%20end%2C%20we%20rode%20through%20the%20morning%20haze%20before%20finally%20coasting%20into%20the%20quiet%20harbor%2C%20which%20looked%20like%20a%20painting%20in%20the%20golden%20morning%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20fueled%20up%20for%20our%20island%20adventure%20at%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20by%20the%20dock.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Monhegan%20Museum%20welcome%20sign%2C%20with%20a%20lighthouse%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1defa02e5a80cfe0502191%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20stop%20off%20the%20boat%20was%20to%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20called%20The%20Barnacle%2C%20which%20sells%20souvenirs%2C%20drinks%2C%20and%20pastries.%20We%20bought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-all-mcdonalds-breakfast-sandwiches-reviewed-photos-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebreakfast%20sandwiches%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20chai%20lattes%2C%20and%20a%20house-made%20energy%20bar%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20we%20needed%20for%20our%20island%20trek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breakfast%2C%20we%20walked%20up%20the%20gravelly%20main%20street%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20we%20stepped%20back%20in%20time.%20We%20saw%20no%20cars%2C%20a%20cart%20selling%20maps%20of%20the%20island%20(with%20just%20a%20box%20to%20collect%20payment%20on%20the%20honor%20system)%2C%20wooden%20signs%2C%20and%20a%20white%20one-room%20schoolhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20short%20climb%20up%20a%20steep%20hill%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20Monhegan%20Museum%20and%20lighthouse%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20incredible%20view%20of%20the%20sleepy%20harbor%20and%20quaint%20houses%20nestled%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20lighthouse%2C%20we%20walked%20through%20a%20butterfly-speckled%20field%20and%20a%20damp%20forest%2C%20reaching%20the%20opposite%20coast%20in%20just%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20east%20side%20of%20Monhegan%20is%20home%20to%20dramatic%20cliffs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emy%20sits%20on%20a%20rock%2C%20looking%20out%20at%20the%20ocean%20and%20cliffs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1df09bb4fb977f35983134%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20my%20childhood%20sailing%20around%20New%20England%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20decade%20of%20adulthood%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthern-california-places-worth-visiting-spots-to-skip-local-recommendations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouthern%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20breathtaking%20bluffs%20on%20Monhegan%20Island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20followed%20uneven%20dirt%20paths%20and%20log%20bridges%20down%20the%20coast%2C%20with%20each%20turn%20unveiling%20gorgeous%20new%20landscapes%3A%20a%20rocky%20cove%2C%20a%20serene%20tide%20pool%2C%20colorful%20wildflowers%2C%20and%20a%20rusted-out%20shipwreck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20special%20event%20provided%20unmatched%20small-town%20charm.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elaborate%20cardboard%20boats%20on%20a%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1df29c2ab5f9757add7ce9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEverywhere%20we%20went%2C%20we%20saw%20hand-drawn%20signs%20for%20the%20annual%20Cardboard%20Regatta%20%E2%80%94%20an%20event%20where%20locals%20gather%20on%20Swim%20Beach%20to%20paddle%20(with%20varying%20success)%20their%20homemade%20tape-and-cardboard%20vessels%20to%20Fish%20Beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20joined%20what%20felt%20like%20the%20whole%20town%20to%20watch%20this%20unique%20local%20event%2C%20which%20typically%20takes%20place%20in%20August.%20I%20felt%20lucky%20to%20have%20stumbled%20upon%20it%20by%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20cooled%20off%20at%20a%20brewery%20on%20the%20island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20flight%20of%20four%20beers%20and%20an%20order%20of%20fried%20pickles%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1df326b4fb977f35983154%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20wandered%20over%20to%20the%20island's%20lobster-trap-lined%20brewery%2C%20Monhegan%20Brewing%20Company%2C%20for%20a%20beer%20flight%20and%20some%20crispy%20pickle%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20ordered%20the%20house-made%20root%20beer%20to%20go%2C%20which%20was%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ride%20home%20was%20on%20a%20bigger%20ferry%20that%20came%20with%20its%20own%20unique%20perks.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20Elizabeth%20Ann%20ferry%20docked%20at%20a%20pier.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1ed7552ab5f9757add7f57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20home%20was%20aboard%20the%20Elizabeth%20Ann%2C%20a%20larger%2C%20more%20modern%20boat%20with%20a%20heated%20cabin%2C%20two%20restrooms%2C%20and%20a%20sightseeing%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20back%20included%20somewhat%20of%20a%20tour%2C%20with%20a%20loop%20around%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20island%20and%20some%20fun%20facts%20shared%20over%20the%20loudspeakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20ride%20was%20a%20little%20less%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20though%20the%20Elizabeth%20Ann%20offered%20comfier%20indoor%20seats%20than%20the%20Laura%20B%2C%20we%20opted%20to%20get%20the%20best%20view%20by%20standing%20at%20the%20bow%20the%20entire%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20the%20trip%20was%20a%20charming%20and%20nostalgic%20adventure.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Historic%20houses%20and%20buildings%20on%20a%20coastal%20island%20in%20Maine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1ee2072ab5f9757add7fb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEmy%20LaCroix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20docking%20in%20Port%20Clyde%2C%20we%20grabbed%20a%20couple%20of%20scoops%20at%20Village%20Ice%20Cream%20and%20enjoyed%20it%20at%20the%20nearby%20Marshall%20Point%20Lighthouse%2C%20famously%20featured%20in%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftom-hanks-paid-for-running-scene-in-forrest-gump-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EForrest%20Gump%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20the%20perfect%20way%20to%20end%20the%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20if%20you're%20seeking%20a%20unique%20day%20trip%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20unplug%2C%20be%20fully%20present%2C%20and%20get%20inspired%2C%20I%20can't%20recommend%20a%20visit%20to%20this%20peaceful%2C%20friendly%2C%20and%20beautiful%20island%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F