20story%20in%20our%20new%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Great%20Coding%20Reset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20is%20terrified%20of%20losing%20their%20job.%20Some%20engineers%20are%20finding%20themselves%20more%20productive%20than%20ever%20thanks%20to%20their%20AI%20copilots.%20Others%20are%20trying%20to%20learn%20soft%20skills%20they%20view%20as%20more%20AI-proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20constant%20is%20that%20everyone%20recognizes%20something%20has%20changed%20and%20is%20adjusting%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoding's%20great%20reckoning%20is%20happening%20as%20Corporate%20America%20undergoes%20an%20overhaul.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20flatter%2C%20efficient%20organizations%20dovetails%20nicely%20with%20the%20democratization%20of%20coding.%20Dave%20in%20sales%20doesn't%20need%20to%20waste%20a%20month%20on%20countless%20meetings%20with%20product%20managers%20and%20technologists%20describing%20a%20new%20tool%20he%20wants.%20Now%20he%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fvibe-mode%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe%20code%20it%20himself%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20exactly%20the%20autonomy%20lots%20of%20organizations%20want%20from%20their%20workers%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftiny-teams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEspecially%20for%20tiny%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20those%20AI%20tools%20could%20supercharge%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20about%20larger%20orgs%20where%20there%20are%20500%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%205%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20Daves%20in%20sales%20building%20their%20own%20tools%3F%20How%20does%20a%20company%20keep%20tabs%20on%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20needs%20to%20know%20what%20those%20tools%20do.%20Someone%20needs%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20secure.%20Someone%20needs%20to%20monitor%20the%20costs.%20Someone%20needs%20to%20determine%20whether%20they're%20creating%20value%20or%20just%20generating%20more%20AI%20slop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20lot%20of%20governance%20for%20an%20era%20supposedly%20defined%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-block-managers-player-coaches-org-leads-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efewer%20managers%20and%20flatter%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20this%20rate%2C%20someone's%20already%20vibe%20coding%20a%20solution%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-management-risks-for-flat-organizations-tech-ai-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780490809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f3ad3b4fb977f35983817%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-management-risks-for-flat-organizations-tech-ai-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coding's%20great%20reckoning%20is%20underway%20as%20Corporate%20America%20pushes%20out%20managers%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20recipe%20for%20disaster.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bank%20of%20America%20accepted%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20internship%20applicants%20this%20year%2C%20but%20AI%20isn't%20shrinking%20the%20class%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brian%20Moynihan%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1edb1f2ab5f9757add7f6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBank%20of%20America%20CEO%20Brian%20Moynihan%20has%20said%20the%20bank%20is%20managing%20staffing%20largely%20through%20attrition.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lamparski%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBank%20of%20America%20received%20around%20240%2C000%20internship%20applications%20for%20fewer%20than%202%2C000%20spots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20number%20of%20summer%20and%20campus%20hires%20is%20roughly%20the%20same%20as%20last%20year%2C%20even%20with%20AI%20automation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20is%20raising%20questions%20about%20how%20to%20teach%20interns%20skills%20they%20now%20won't%20naturally%20learn%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20job-pocalypse%20hasn't%20come%20for%20Bank%20of%20America's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-summer-internship-advice-success-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esummer%20internship%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20good%20luck%20trying%20to%20land%20a%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20hired%20nearly%204%2C000%20summer%20interns%20and%20full-time%20campus%20recruits%20this%20year%2C%20split%20roughly%20evenly%20between%20the%20two%2C%20in%20line%20with%20last%20year's%20numbers.%20Around%20240%2C000%20people%20applied%20for%20fewer%20than%202%2C000%20internships%2C%20Josh%20Bronstein%2C%20the%20global%20head%20of%20talent%2C%20said%2C%20bringing%20the%20application%20rate%20to%20around%200.8%25.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20said%20that%20applications%20ticked%20upwards%20this%20year%2C%20likely%20both%20because%20of%20AI%20tools%20that%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20apply%20and%20a%20genuine%20increase%20in%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Brian%20Moynihan%20has%20previously%20said%20the%20firm%2C%20which%20employs%20more%20than%20213%2C000%20people%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-citi-goldman-bofa-wells-ai-impact-headcounts-2026%23brian-moynihan-bank-of-america-ceo-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20operational%20and%20processing%20roles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20continues%20to%20hire%20in%20key%20areas%20like%20relationship%20management%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20cybersecurity.%20Bronstein%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20junior%20hires%20remain%20a%20strategic%20priority%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20bank%20looks%20for%20%26quot%3Bcareer-minded%26quot%3B%20applicants%20who%20can%20see%20themselves%20staying%20there.%20The%20%26quot%3Bvast%20majority%26quot%3B%20of%20interns%20typically%20get%20a%20return%20offer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20being%20very%20intentional%20and%20thoughtful%20about%20the%20investments%20that%20we're%20making%20for%20the%20long%20term%20through%20hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20includes%20our%20campus%20class.%20We%20believe%20this%20is%20an%20important%20pipeline.%20It%20is%20a%20deliberate%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20said%20that%20while%20he%20can't%20predict%20whether%20or%20how%20the%20number%20of%20young%20hires%20will%20change%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bit's%20hard%20to%20have%20a%20crystal%20ball%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20financial%20sector%20has%20weathered%20other%20waves%20of%20technological%20change%2C%20and%20the%20bank%20remains%20committed%20to%20entry-level%20talent.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-summer-interns-ai-banks-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThis%20summer's%20interns%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20entering%20a%20transforming%20Wall%20Street%2C%20as%20AI%20reshuffles%20workflows%20and%20career%20trajectories.%20While%20interns%20used%20to%20help%20draft%20the%20pitch%20decks%20and%20build%20the%20models%20that%20AI%20tools%20can%20now%20handle%2C%20many%20will%20now%20be%20expected%20to%20use%20AI%20for%20those%20tasks%20and%20devote%20time%20to%20higher-order%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271911d7e-2eee-4d2c-8d22-e35becf7782d%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20changing%20recruitment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBronstein%20said%20that%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhalf-life%20of%20technical%20skills%26quot%3B%20continues%20to%20shrink%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20is%20looking%20for%20yo