Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20build%20products%20that%20shaped%20how%20people%20lived%20and%20learned.%20I%20craved%20a%20faster%20pace%2C%20bigger%20challenges%2C%20and%20proof%20that%20someone%20like%20me%20could%20succeed%20in%20an%20industry%20known%20for%20closing%20doors%20on%20outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20rejection%20made%20that%20dream%20feel%20further%20away%2C%20but%20I%20kept%20pushing.%20I%20felt%20confident%20that%20once%20I'd%20broken%20into%20tech%20and%20found%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20job%2C%20I'd%20stick%20with%20it%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20landed%20the%20tech%20role%20I'd%20been%20working%20toward%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20vindication.%20I%20was%20proud%2C%20relieved%2C%20and%20confident%20that%20all%20the%20struggle%20had%20been%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20see%20was%20that%20I%20was%20stepping%20into%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-new-york-dream-job-moved-to-colorado-with-family-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edream%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20exact%20moment%20my%20life%20was%20already%20collapsing%20under%20its%20own%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20didn't%20realize%20I%20was%20clinging%20to%20an%20outdated%20idea%20of%20what%20a%20career%20should%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22171a1b3d-d32f-46a2-b3c1-321189e5086b%5C%22%3EThe%20dream%20and%20the%20burnout%20arrived%20together%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20office%20space%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a16f1422ab5f9757add4ba3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalking%20away%20was%20difficult%20and%20felt%20like%20admitting%20defeat%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20my%20well-being.%3Cp%3ELuis%20Alvarez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20that%20job%20while%20finishing%20my%20MBA.%20To%20everyone%20else%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20momentum.%20To%20me%2C%20it%20was%20an%20exhausting%20performance%20of%20holding%20everything%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20days%20were%20spent%20learning%20a%20new%20industry.%20Assignments%20and%20deadlines%20consumed%20my%20nights.%20I%20kept%20telling%20myself%20I%20could%20do%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20body%20disagreed.%20My%20hair%20started%20falling%20out%20in%20clumps.%20I%20woke%20up%20exhausted%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20I%20slept.%20A%20constant%20tightness%20settled%20in%20my%20chest%2C%20even%20on%20ordinary%20days.%20I%20convinced%20myself%20the%20stress%20was%20temporary%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyale-graduate-moved-back-to-low-income-home-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20price%20of%20ambition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20finally%20making%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20afternoon%2C%20my%20boss%20called%20me%20in.%20Her%20tone%20was%20measured%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20something%20was%20coming.%20The%20company%20was%20restructuring.%20My%20role%20was%20at%20risk.%20Then%20she%20offered%20me%20a%20choice%3A%20accept%20a%20layoff%20package%20or%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20didn't%20really%20feel%20like%20an%20option.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it%20had%20become%20impossible%20to%20ignore%20what%20I%20had%20been%20feeling%20for%20months%3A%20the%20environment%20wasn't%20sustainable%2C%20and%20the%20workload%20was%20pushing%20me%20past%20my%20limits%20while%20I%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20finish%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecognizing%20that%20truth%20was%20both%20validating%20and%20devastating.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20it%20confirmed%20I%20hadn't%20imagined%20the%20pressure.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20it%20forced%20me%20to%20confront%20just%20how%20much%20I%20had%20sacrificed%20to%20hold%20onto%20an%20idea%20of%20success%20that%20wasn't%20actually%20serving%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20cracked%20open%20a%20question%20I'd%20been%20too%20afraid%20to%20ask%3A%20What%20if%20the%20career%20path%20I'd%20been%20chasing%20so%20desperately%20wasn't%20actually%20the%20one%20I%20needed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22833b31f8-3ed0-4098-993f-f2807b370ded%5C%22%3EThe%20layoff%20that%20felt%20like%20failure%20became%20freedom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20accepted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-offers-us-workers-up-to-26-weeks-severance-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elayoff%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20it%20felt%20like%20watching%20my%20dream%20evaporate%20just%20as%20I'd%20reached%20it.%20I'd%20fought%20so%20hard%20to%20break%20into%20tech%2C%20only%20to%20leave%20burned%20out%2C%20unwell%2C%20and%20uncertain%20about%20what%20came%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20initial%20shock%20faded%2C%20something%20unexpected%20happened%3A%20I%20had%20space%20to%20breathe.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years%2C%20I%20let%20myself%20rest%20without%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20body%20began%20to%20heal.%20My%20hair%20stopped%20falling%20out.%20My%20energy%20returned.%20I%20rediscovered%20parts%20of%20myself%20I'd%20abandoned%20in%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20forced%20pause%20gave%20me%20clarity%2C%20and%20when%20I%20started%20working%20again%2C%20I%20approached%20it%20very%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20returning%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-employers-quiet-quitting-contractors-part-time-gig-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraditional%20full-time%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20began%20taking%20on%20projects%20on%20my%20own%20terms%20and%20chose%20work%20aligned%20with%20my%20values.%20I%20built%20a%20schedule%20that%20protects%20my%20health%20instead%20of%20sacrificing%20it%20and%20embraced%20flexibility%20without%20apologizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9239f12-1d7c-4ebb-b71b-4a71d44c40cd%5C%22%3EI%20realized%20that%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20destroy%20myself%20to%20build%20a%20meaningful%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20graduation%20robe%2C%20blue%20dress%2C%20smiling%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a16f1022e5a80cfe04ff124%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELosing%20my%20dream%20job%20wasn't%20the%20end.%20It%20was%20the%20reset%20I%20desperately%20needed.%3Cp%3EAshley%20Rivera%20Mercado%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20laid%20off%20from%20the%20job%20I%20thought%20would%20define%20my%20career%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20was%20painful%20and%20destabilizing.%20However%2C%20it%20gave%20me%20a%20valuable%20chance%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-canada-for-love-rebuild-my-career-identity-trailing-spouse-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erebuild%20my%20professional%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20balance%2C%20intention%2C%20and%20actual%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20taught%20me%20that%20a%20career%20path%20isn't%20a%20straight%20line%20you%20draw%20once%20and%20follow%20forever%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20redraw%20it%20continuously%2C%20with%20more%20information%20and%20clearer%20priorities%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%20far%20more%20liberating%3A%20Careers%20evolve%20as%20we%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20OK%20to%20pivot%20if%20the%20industry%20that%20excited%20you%20at%2025%20drains%20you%20at%2030.%20The%20role%20you%20fought%20to%20get%20might%20teach%20you%20exactly%20what%20you%20don't%20want%2C%20and%20skills%20you%20build%20in%20one%20chapter%20often%20become%20unexpected%20assets%20in%20the%20next.%20None%20of%20this%20is%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20this%20experience%20shattered%20myths%20I%20had%20carried%20since%20college%3A%20that%20successful%20people%20find%20their%20path%20early%20and%20stick%20to%20it%20forever%2C%20that%20pivoting%20means%20failing%2C%20and%20that%20changing%20your%20mind%20makes%20you%20unreliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20my%2020s%20believing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-regret-leads-pr-pro-teaching-business-success-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20something%20to%20fear%20or%20avoid.%20Now%20I%20see%20them%20as%20necessary%20recalibrations.%20Each%20shift%20teaches%20you%20more%20about%20what%20energizes%20you%2C%20what%20matters%20to%20you%2C%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20work%20allows%20you%20to%20show%20up%20as.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-laid-off-led-me-to-better-job-saved-health-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780489561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a16f0e3b4fb977f35980081%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-laid-off-led-me-to-better-job-saved-health-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20being%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20dream%20career%20was%20difficult%2C%20it%20was%20good%20for%20my%20health.%20It%20also%20helped%20me%20rebuild%20my%20life%20and%20find%20a%20better%20job%20for%20me.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ashley%20Rivera%20Mercado)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20end%20of%20Trump's%20'weaponisation'%20fund%20is%20another%20sign%20Republicans%20are%20fighting%20back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780489531000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fb51b%2Flive%2F883d9c70-5f44-11f1-ae51-c396b5163a64.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc87q9d7r57yo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%241.8bn%20fund%20would%20have%20paid%20people%20the%20Trump%20administration%20decided%20were%20unjus