%2Finflammatory-foods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efoods%20she%20considers%20inflammatory%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20red%20meat%20and%20sugar%2C%20tend%20to%20worsen%20her%20symptoms.%20Conversely%2C%20when%20she%20eats%20mostly%20whole%20foods%20like%20vegetables%20and%20sardines%2C%20she%20feels%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20leafy%20greens%2C%20fish%2C%20I%20have%20no%20problems%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Rowland%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b219e88c-611a-4091-91fd-743a4b1a2d18%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20sets%20boundaries%20around%20stress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225439%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Essential%20oil%20bottle%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f1565b4fb977f35983607%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERowland%20sometimes%20wears%20essential%20oils%20on%20her%20collarbone%20for%20a%20soothing%20effect.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Falls%20Commercial%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERowland%20said%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Feczema-vs-psoriasis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeczema%20flare-up%20triggers%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20stress.%20%26quot%3BStress%20will%20get%20me%20every%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20I'm%20eating%20that%20clean%2C%20it%20could%20be%20one%20thing%20that%20day%20that%20sets%20me%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer%20understands%20how%20to%20course-correct%20when%20her%20stress%20levels%20rise%20beyond%20her%20comfort%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bath%20is%20the%20greatest%20thing%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMeditation%20usually%20helps%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20likes%20to%20put%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Faromatherapy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%