k%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20weekly%20marketing%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20best%20a%20'C%2C'%20probably%20a%20'D.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20Jon%20Mandel%20says%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20would%20grade%20the%20current%20state%20of%20transparency%20on%20Madison%20Avenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20Mandel%2C%20formerly%20CEO%20of%20the%20WPP%20media%20agency%20Mediacom%2C%20publicly%20alleged%20kickbacks%20were%20widespread%20in%20the%20ad%20industry.%20His%20claims%20set%20off%20a%20firestorm%2C%20with%20one%20story%20at%20the%20time%20questioning%20whether%20he%20was%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmumbrella.com.au%2Fthe-most-hated-man-in-global-advertising-jon-mandel-on-how-media-value-banks-are-destroying-advertising-365406%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20hated%20man%20in%20advertising%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20of%20National%20Advertisers%20followed%20Mandel's%20claims%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fana-report-alleges-widespread-ad-agency-kickback-schemes-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eblockbuster%202016%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20said%20undisclosed%20kickbacks%20and%20rebates%20were%20%26quot%3Bpervasive%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20US%20media%20agency%20ecosystem.%20Agencies%20at%20the%20time%20broadly%20denied%20wrongdoing%2C%20but%20the%20report%20became%20a%20lightning%20rod%2C%20compelling%20CMOs%20to%20launch%20a%20wave%20of%20agency%20audits%20and%20redraft%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandel%20told%20me%20that%20many%20of%20the%20issues%20he%20presented%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20when%20he%20would%20have%20given%20the%20industry%20a%20transparency%20score%20of%20%26quot%3Ban%20F%20when%20everyone%20thought%20it%20was%20an%20A%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20have%20improved%20as%20CMOs%20have%20become%20better%20at%20scrutinizing%20their%20agency%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandel%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20marketing%20and%20tech%20companies%2C%20said%20his%20biggest%20bugbear%20about%20the%20industry%20now%20is%20%26quot%3Bprincipal%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20takes%20many%20forms%2C%20but%20at%20its%20essence%2C%20it's%20when%20agencies%20purchase%20a%20large%20volume%20of%20media%20%E2%80%94%20spots%20where%20ads%20can%20run%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20resell%20it%20to%20their%20clients%2C%20and%20make%20an%20undisclosed%20margin%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20model%20say%20it%20can%20create%20conflicts%20of%20interest%20for%20agencies%2C%20which%20could%20be%20incentivized%20to%20steer%20marketers%20toward%20media%20the%20agency%20has%20already%20bought%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20inventory%20best%20suited%20to%20clients'%20campaign%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20non-transparent%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgencies%20argue%20that%20principal%20media%20is%20often%20more%20cost-effective%20for%20clients%20than%20buying%20the%20media%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20CMOs%20are%20happy%20to%20participate%20so%20long%20as%20it%20performs%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomnicom-ceo-john-wren-ipg-merger-ai-job-cuts-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOmnicom%20CEO%20John%20Wren%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20March%20that%20clients%20are%20%26quot%3Btriply%20aware%26quot%3B%20about%20what%20they're%20signing%20up%20for%20with%20principal%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20because%20it%20drives%20value%20for%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Omnicom%20CFO%20Philip%20Angelastro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMadison%20and%20Wall%2C%20the%20advisory%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20recently%20estimated%20that%20principal%20media%20accounts%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20single-digit%20or%20low%20double-digit%26quot%3B%20share%20of%20large-brand%20and%20agency%20activity%20in%20the%20US.%20A%20survey%20released%20in%20March%20by%20the%20ANA%20suggested%20principal%20media%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20with%2058%25%20of%20respondents%20saying%20that%20they%20had%20used%20it%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20up%20from%2047%25%20the%20prior%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20recent%20ANA%20survey%20found%2043%25%20of%20advertisers%20had%20concerns%20about%20the%20level%20of%20transparency%20with%20their%20media%20agency.%20The%20most%20frequently%20cited%20reason%3F%20Principal%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandel%20thinks%20that%20principal%20media%20should%20be%20rebranded%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20that%20I%20find%20most%20upsetting%20about%20all%20of%20this%20is%20not%20that%20it's%20still%20going%20on%2C%20because%20it%20still%20is%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20keep%20calling%20it%20principal%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandel%20said.%20He%20contended%20that%20agencies%20are%20not%20truly%20acting%20as%20%26quot%3Bprincipals%26quot%3B%20at%20all%2C%20and%20instead%20leverage%20the%20full%20pool%20of%20their%20clients'%20budgets%20without%20assuming%20meaningful%20risk%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgencies%20would%20argue%20that%20if%20they%20use%20their%20own%20capital%20to%20secure%20ad%20inventory%20and%20don't%20resell%20it%2C%20they're%20still%20on%20the%20hook%20to%20pay%20those%20publishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandel%20said%20agencies%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20open%20up%20the%20books%20to%20marketers%20about%20the%20inventory%20they%20are%20selling%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20not%20disclosing%20the%20profits%20they%20are%20making%20from%20principal%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20food%20company%20and%20you%20are%20getting%20raw%20ingredients%2C%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20profit%20margin%20of%20the%20company%20that's%20supplying%20whatever%20raw%20ingredient%2C%20but%20you%20have%20the%20right%20to%20check%20the%20quality%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20factory%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20landscape%20has%20evolved%20dramatically%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20streaming%20TV%2C%20retail%20media%2C%20data%20clean%20rooms%2C%20and%20AI%20now%20thrown%20into%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMandel%20said%20the%20changes%20serve%20up%20a%20%26quot%3BWhac-A-Mole%26quot%3B%20for%20CMOs%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20holding%20their%20agencies%20accountable%20and%20double-checking%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20media%20they're%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20advice%3A%20Employ%20media%20specialists%2C%20ensure%20audit%20rights%20are%20written%20into%20contracts%2C%20and%20treat%20contracts%20as%20living%2C%20changing%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20'trust%2C%20but%20verify%2C'%26quot%3B%20Mandel%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20verify%2C%20verify%2C%20verify%2C%20and%20trust%20no%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-mandel-ad-agency-transparency-principal-media-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780488001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f1e092ab5f9757add8206%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-mandel-ad-agency-transparency-principal-media-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jon%20Mandel%2C%20who%20set%20off%20a%20firestorm%20in%202016%20with%20a%20presentation%20about%20alleged%20agency%20kickbacks%2C%20has%20beef%20with%20principal%20media%20trading.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pink%20Teases%20Tony%20Awards%20Hosting%20Plans%3A%20%E2%80%98There%20Will%20Be%20Stunts%2C%20and%20Not%20Just%20for%20Me%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780488000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236765281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Generally%20speaking%2C%20the%20announcement%20of%20Grammy-winning%20pop%20powerhouse%20Pink%20as%20the%20host%20of%20the%2079th%20Tony%20Awards%20on%20Sunday%20was%20met%20with%20two%20immediate%20reactions%3A%20a)%20will%20she%20fly%2C%20and%20b)%2C%20why%20her%3F%20While%20Pink%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctheater%20kid%E2%80%9D%20growing%20up%20(more%20on%20that%20shortly)%2C%20the%20second%20question%20was%20actually%20her%20initial%20reaction%20as%20well%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jem%20Aswad%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jim%20Sheridan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Re-Creation%E2%80%99%20Closes%20U.S.%20With%20Kino%20Lorber%20While%20Latido%20Sells%20Pregnant%20Trans%20Man%20Drama%20%E2%80%989%20Moons%E2%80%99%20to%20Half%20the%20World%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780487878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236765605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Kino%20Lorber%20U.S.%20pick-up%20on%20Jim%20Sheridan%20and%20David%20Merriman%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CRe-Creation%E2%80%9D%20heads%20sales%20for%20Madrid-based%20Latido%20Films%20at%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20Cannes%20which%20also%20take%20in%20theatrical%20deals%20in%20major%20markets%20over%20half%20the%20world%20for%20pregnant%20trans%20man%20drama%20%E2%80%9C9%20Moons.%E2%80%9D%20In%20further%20notable%20transactions%2C%20Gael%20Garc%C3%ADa%20Bernal%2FNatalia%20Oreiro%20romantic%20drama%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20Between%20Us%E2%80%9D%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22John%20Hopewell%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20stopped%20trying%20to%20make%20my%20husband%20love%20working%20out.%20Letting%20go%20of%20my%20'fitness-couple%20fantasy'%20helped%20our%20marriage.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222172%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lorraine%20C.%20Ladish%20and%20her%20husband%20on%20a%20hike%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d9076b4fb977f35982bdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221629%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20been%20married%20to%20my%20husband%20for%20almost%2017%20years.%3Cp%3ELorraine%20C.%20Ladish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFitness%20is%20the%20one%20area%20where%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20don't%20see%20eye%20to%20eye.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20views%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-high-intensity-training-workout-2017-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintense%20regimen%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20excessive%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he%20could%20be%20doing%20more%20to%20support%20his%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20we%20accepted%20our%20different%20activity%20levels%2C%20our%20marriage%20improved.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20I%20see%20a%20couple%20working%20out%20together%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20wonder%20what%20it%20would%20be%20like%20to%20share%20an%20exercise%20routine%20with%20a%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20in%20common%2C%20from%20being%20bilingual%20to%20working%20in%20creative%20fields.%20Fitness%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20one%20thing%20we've%20always%20approached%20differently%20during%20our%20nearly%2017-year%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20working%20out%20since%20I%20was%20a%20teenager.%20Now%20I'm%20in%20my%2060s%20and%20strength%20train%20for%20two%20hours%20three%20times%20per%20week%2C%20walk%20our%20dog%20daily%2C%20practice%20yoga%20three%20times%20per%20week%2C%20and%20train%20for%20the%20occasional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-train-for-a-5k-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5K%20race%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20didn't%20start%20exercising%20until%20he%20was%20well%20into%20his%2040s.%20Now%2C%20at%2061%2C%20he%20goes%20to%20the%20gym%20three%20times%20per%20week%2C%20finishing%20each%20session%20in%20less%20than%2030%20minutes.%20I%20feel%20like%20he%20could%20do%20more%2C%20but%20he's%20content%20with%20his%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20supported%20me%20as%20I've%20trained%20for%20a%20half-marathon%20and%20several%20shorter%20races%2C%20become%20a%20certified%20yoga%20instructor%2C%20and%20learned%20to%20do%20pull-ups.%20That%20said%2C%20he%20doesn't%20share%20(or%20completely%20understand)%20my%20desire%20to%20accomplish%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsetting-physical-goals-helped-me-get-older-essay-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintense%20fitness%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20him%2C%20my%20lengthy%20workouts%20seem%20excessive%2C%20but%20to%20me%2C%20they're%20a%20nonnegotiable%20part%20of%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b706060-b093-465a-ad80-4bcb017ccec8%5C%22%3EEarly%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20push%20my%20fitness-couple%20fantasy%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we've%20since%20accepted%20our%20differences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lorraine%20C.%20Ladish%20and%20her%20husband%20traveling%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d91b02e5a80cfe0501c78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224030%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20our%20different%20activity%20levels%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20travel%20well%20together.%3Cp%3ELorraine%20C.%20Ladish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20got%20together%20and%20blended%20our%20families%2C%20I%20signed%20us%20all%20up%20for%20a%20nearby%20racquetball%20club%20with%20a%20gym%20and%20lap%20pool.%20I%20figured%20it'd%20be%20a%20fun%20way%20for%20us%20to%20spend%20time%20together%20and%20stay%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20go%20as%20planned.%20The%20kids%20had%20a%20blast%2C%20but%20my%20husband%20would%20leave%20before%20I%20even%20finished%20warming%20up.%20If%20I%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-education-teaching-job-to-be-barre-fitness-instructor-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20fitness%20instructor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20corrected%20his%20form%2C%20he'd%20resent%20it.%20I%20realized%20he%20wasn't%20working%20out%20to%20excel%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20hours%20in%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sometimes%20bothered%20me%20that%20he%20didn't%20invest%20more%20time%20and%20energy%20in%20fitness%2C%20and%20also%20that%20we%20couldn't%20enjoy%20it%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20see%20eye-to-eye%20on%20pretty%20much%20everything%20except%20fitness%2C%20I%20eventually%20realized%20I%20had%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20fantasy%20that%20paddleboarding%2C%20hiking%2C%20swimming%20laps%2C%20or%20some%20other%20activity%20would%20finally%20turn%20us%20into%20a%20couple%20that%20enjoyed%20exercising%20together%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20want%20to%20take%20our%20dog%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaily-hour-long-walk-impacts-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20walk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20go%20by%20myself.%20I%20reserve%20walks%20with%20my%20husband%20for%20the%20days%20I'm%20OK%20turning%20around%20after%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prioritize%20fitness%2C%20so%20if%20I%20have%20to%20push%20back%20dinner%20or%20skip%20an%20event%20to%20fit%20in%20a%20workout%2C%20I%20will.%20When%20life%20gets%20busy%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20to%20come%20off%20his%20calendar%20is%20usually%20a%20workout.%20I%20decided%20to%20stop%20trying%20to%20make%20him%20love%20intense%20exercise%2C%20and%20he%20accepted%20that%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20dial%20back%20my%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3d39f9c-8fd1-4866-b071-ee1fabf2aac6%5C%22%3EOur%20marriage%20improved%20when%20we%20found%20joint%20hobbies%20outside%20of%20the%20gym%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222926%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lorraine%20C.%20Ladish%20and%20her%20husband%20performing%20improv%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d91e5b4fb977f35982be7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20spend%20plenty%20of%20quality%20time%20together%20doing%20activities%20like%20improv%20classes.%3Cp%3ELorraine%20C.%20Ladish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20my%20past%20partners%20have%20been%20fitness%20buffs%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20it%20would%20be%20like%20to%20share%20a%20life%20with%20someone%20as%20dedicated%20to%20exercise%20as%20I%20am.%20However%2C%20I'd%20take%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-your-partner-is-marriage-material-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehusband's%20values%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dependability%2C%20and%20willingness%20to%20work%20things%20out%20over%20a%20desire%20to%20match%20my%20fitness%20goals%20any%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20accepted%20his%20laid-back%20approach%20to%20fitness%20and%20he%20accepted%20my%20commitment%20to%20working%20out%2C%20exercise%20stopped%20being%20a%20point%20of%20contention.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-consistent-workout-habit-fitness-coach-tips-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20consider%20the%20bare%20minimum%20and%20he%20considers%20obsessive%20%E2%80%94%20is%20nonnegotiable.%20I%20now%20realize%20that%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20work%20out%20with%20my%20husband%20to%20feel%20connected%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20things%20we%20enjoy%20together%2C%20such%20as%20discussing%20creative%20projects%2C%20traveling%2C%20and%20taking%20improv%20and%20acting%20classes.%20Now%20that%20we've%20both%20accepted%20the%20other's%20approach%20to%20fitness%2C%20we%20don't%20argue%20about%20it%20and%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraits-every-happy-couple-has-in-common-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappier%20as%20a%20couple%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarrying-someone-who-works-out-less-fitness-gap-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780487821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1d8fbf2e5a80cfe0501c64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarrying-someone-who-works-out-less-fitness-gap-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20thinks%20my%20exercise%20routine%20is%20obsessive%2C%20but%20I%20consider%20it%20the%20bare%20minimum.%20Over%20time%2C%20we've%20accepted%20our%20different%20fitness%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lorraine%20C.%20Ladish)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TVK-led%20alliance%20allots%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20to%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780487765000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131483741%2Cimgsize-1241566.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftvk-led-alliance-allots-tamil-nadu-rajya-sabha-seat-to-congress%2Farticleshow%2F131483633.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Tamilaga%20Vettri%20Kazhagam-led%20alliance%20has%20allocated%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20its%20partner%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20This%20decision%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20biennial%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20June%2018.%20The%20Con