%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20silos%20are%20a%20problem%20for%20brands%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-intelligent-search-box-ai-mode-features-information-agents-io-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20search%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Semrush%20said.%20Large%20language%20models%20are%20pulling%20data%20from%20multiple%20sources%2C%20including%20corporate%20websites'%20blogs%2C%20news%20articles%2C%20Reddit%20chatter%2C%20and%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20companies%20were%20able%20to%20operate%20in%20a%20fairly%20siloed%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20Leigh%20McKenzie%2C%20director%20of%20online%20visibility%20at%20Semrush%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20brand%20team%20was%20doing%20something%20on%20social%20media%20that%20was%20different%20to%20what%20the%20SEO%20team%20was%20doing%20on%20the%20blog%2C%20and%20the%20customer%20success%20team%20didn't%20really%20pay%20too%20much%20attention%20to%20how%20many%20people%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20brand%20on%20Reddit%2C%26quot%3B%20McKenzie%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20inconsistencies%20in%20how%20companies%20talk%20about%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20consumers%20talk%20about%20them%20%E2%80%94%20can%20lead%20to%20inaccuracies%20in%20how%20chatbots%20and%20search%20platforms%20represent%20their%20brands%2C%20potentially%20affecting%20their%20visibility%20on%20these%20channels%20relative%20to%20competitors%2C%20Semrush%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20brands%20that%20aren't%20joined%20up%20internally%20may%20not%20be%20measuring%20their%20AI%20search%20efforts%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fl1RJq%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bar%20Chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fl1RJq%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20that%20are%20executing%20best%20in%20AI%20search%20right%20now%20have%20been%20making%20sure%20their%20brands%20show%20up%20across%20all%20these%20channels%20in%20a%20much%20more%20cohesive%20way%2C%20McKenzie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20ChatGPT's%20debut%20in%202022%2C%20brands%20have%20been%20scrambling%20to%20figure%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-reshapes-seo-fueling-geo-gold-rush-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20engine%20optimization%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20GEO%20%E2%80%94%20ensuring%20AI%20answer%20engines%20accurately%20surface%20their%20products%2C%20services%2C%20and%20messaging.%20With%20AI%20companies%20regularly%20updating%20their%20models%20and%20search%20increasingly%20moving%20from%20links%20to%20answers%2C%20marketers%20are%20having%20to%20rewrite%20their%20SEO%20playbooks%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-helped-pivot-from-software-engineering-to-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHubSpot%2C%20a%20customer%20relationship%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ranks%20third%20in%20the%20business%20and%20professional%20services%20category%20in%20Semrush's%20latest%20quarterly%20brand%20visibility%20index%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHubSpot%20CMO%20Kipp%20Bodnar%20said%20the%20company%20never%20treated%20answer%20engine%20optimization%20as%20a%20separate%20team%20or%20strategy%20from%20SEO%2C%20and%20instead%20approached%20AI%20visibility%20as%20an%20evolution%20of%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20integrated%20approach%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20move%20faster%2C%20avoid%20duplicate%20work%2C%20and%20create%20a%20more%20consistent%20experience%20across%20both%20traditional%20search%20and%20AI-driven%20discovery%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodnar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20issues%20they'd%20experienced%20with%20AI%20search%2C%2037%25%20of%20the%20marketers%20Semrush%20surveyed%20said%20competitors%20were%20mentioned%20more%20often%20than%20their%20brand.%20Thirty%20percent%20said%20their%20brand%20was%20described%20inaccurately%2C%20and%2029%25%20said%20their%20positioning%20was%20unclear%20or%20generic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20taking%20different%20approaches%20to%20who%20should%20be%20responsible%20for%20AI%20search.%20While%2018%25%20of%20the%20companies%20Semrush%20surveyed%20said%20they%20have%20a%20dedicated%20GEO%20specialist%20or%20team%2C%2016%25%20said%20it%20sat%20within%20the%20SEO%20department%2C%2015%25%20said%20their%20content%20teams%20looked%20after%20it%2C%20and%2014%25%20said%20responsibility%20was%20shared%20across%20multiple%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Semrush%2C%20the%20SEO%20team%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20more%20prominent%20role%20within%20the%20corporate%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20much%20bigger%20seat%20at%20the%20leadership%20table%20than%20I%20had%20two%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20McKenzie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemrush's%20study%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20CMO%20Insider%2C%20surveyed%20481%20US%20marketers%2C%20business%20owners%2C%20and%20SEO%20professionals%20in%20April%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-strategies-hampered-by-corporate-silos-semrush-study-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780487402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f20ea2e5a80cfe0502727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-strategies-hampered-by-corporate-silos-semrush-study-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20study%20shines%20a%20light%20on%20how%20corporate%20silos%20can%20lead%20to%20issues%20with%20how%20brands%20show%20up%20in%20AI%20search%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20says%20his%20heart%20sank%20when%20he%20returned%20to%20work%20after%20son%20Vihaan's%20birth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780487127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131483559%2Cimgsize-70946.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-says-his-heart-sank-when-he-returned-to-work-after-son-vihaans-birth-appreciates-his-parents-more-after-becoming-a-father%2Farticleshow%2F131483537.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131483537.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%2C%20a%20new%20father%20to%20son%20Vihaan%2C%20reflects%20on%20how%20parenthood%20has%20deepened%20his%20appreciation%20for%20his%20own%20upbringing%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20leading%20by%20example.%20He%20also%20shared%20the%20emotional%20difficulty%20of%20his%20first%20separation%20from%20his%20child%20for%20a%20work%20commitment%2C%20now%20understanding%20parents'%20feelings%20about%20children%20growing%20up%20quickly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20post%20LinkedIn%20comedy%20skits%20to%20help%20my%20marketing%20company%20get%20new%20clients.%20Here's%20what%20works%20and%20what%20I%20won't%20do.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20Hayes%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f138c2e5a80cfe050269f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHenry%20Hayes%2C%20VP%20of%20mar