inkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7404079334715531264%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELove%2C%20Actually%20-%20but%20for%20marketers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7421473312989466624%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBatman%3A%20The%20Dark%20Knight%20-%20but%20for%20marketers%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20be%20doing%20%26quot%3BPirates%20of%20the%20Caribbean%20-%20but%20for%20marketers%26quot%3B%20at%20Cannes%20Lions%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20snowballed%20into%20a%20weird%20and%20brilliant%20world%20where%20we%20are%20actually%20getting%20good%20leads%20off%20the%20back%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a700e014-b765-4abf-8724-706dd6ebd387%5C%22%3EWhy%20my%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%20spoof%20resonated%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fhenry-hayes-235028104_grand-theft-auto-vice-city-but-for-marketers-ugcPost-7464944835901325312-VUrJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAASBCJcBqqkqQxOOdVFYt_MkgR-tHxhtLnc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrand%20Theft%20Auto%20Vice%20City%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20marketers%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20by%20far%20our%20biggest%20project%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7464944835901325312%3Fcompact%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20used%20our%20own%20internal%20AI%20tool%2C%20PIP%2C%20to%20put%20together%20scripts%20for%20me%20based%20on%20integrations%20we%20have%20with%20LinkedIn%20on%20our%20best-performing%20posts%2C%20and%20the%20best-performing%20posts%20I've%20put%20out%20on%20my%20own%20personal%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20LinkedIn%2C%20you%20can't%20be%20as%20nuanced%20as%20you%20can%20be%20on%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok.%20You%20have%20to%20go%20for%20the%20big%20stuff.%20The%20bigger%20the%20name%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20game%2C%20the%20better%20the%20visual%20cues%2C%20the%20more%20people%20understand%20the%20narrative%2C%20and%20the%20more%20chance%20you%20have%20of%20it%20going%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%20works%20well%20is%20that%20straight%20away%2C%20you%20see%20me%20running%20around%20like%20I'm%20in%20the%20game.%20You%20then%20see%20me%20getting%20someone%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20and%20that%20is%20a%20visual%20cue%20that%20everyone%20who's%20played%20the%20game%20understands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soundtrack%20of%20Vice%20City%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20about%20the%20game%20for%20me.%20We%20know%20our%20ideal%20customer%20profile%20%E2%80%94%20a%20CMO%20or%20VP%20of%20marketing%20aged%2035%20to%2055%20%E2%80%94%20would%20resonate%20with%20that%20kind%20of%20music.%20Hall%20%26amp%3B%20Oates.%20Grandmaster%20Flash.%20Talk%20Talk.%20Luther%20Vandross.%20Oliver%20Cheatham.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221553266-85c7-4de2-816b-dcba3b9dbb02%5C%22%3EWhy%20I'll%20never%20use%20AI%20to%20generate%20my%20videos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20put%20AI%20into%20the%20video.%20We%20use%20AI%20a%20lot%20in%20ideation%20and%20scriptwriting%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20in%20post-production%20and%20editing%2C%20but%20I'll%20never%20use%20it%20in%20the%20visual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20a%20creator%2C%20I%20want%20people%20to%20find%20me%20credible%20as%20an%20individual%2C%20so%20they%20ultimately%20become%20potential%20clients%20of%20Passionfruit.%20They've%20got%20to%20see%20the%20rawness%20and%20credibility%20in%20my%20work.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20VP%2C%20SVP%2C%20or%20CMO%20of%20a%20big%20business%20to%20engage%20with%20my%20content%2C%20and%20the%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20putting%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20fans%20of%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto.%20I%20spent%20a%20bit%20of%20time%20around%20the%20house%20and%20in%20the%20park%2C%20seeing%20how%20I%20could%20do%20the%20character%20movements.%20Then%20I%20downloaded%20from%20YouTube%20the%20entire%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%3A%20Vice%20City%20runthrough%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20four%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20long.%20I%20watched%20it%20on%20the%20plane%20to%20Miami%20so%20I%20could%20learn%20the%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20said%20you%20get%20nowhere%20near%20the%20amount%20of%20traction%20that%20you%20used%20to%20on%20LinkedIn.%20The%20amount%20of%20effort%20I%20put%20into%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20two%20or%20three%20videos%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20would%20translate%20to%20a%20lot%20more%20followers%20on%20TikTok%20than%20I%20currently%20have%20on%20LinkedIn.%20But%20I'm%20not%20out%20there%20to%20make%20clickbait.%20I'm%20presenting%20this%20stuff%20for%20the%20marketing%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketer-makes-comedy-skits-for-linkedin-to-acquire-clients-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780486801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f13392e5a80cfe050269a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketer-makes-comedy-skits-for-linkedin-to-acquire-clients-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Henry%20Hayes%20is%20gaining%20traction%20and%20new%20client%20leads%20by%20posting%20comedy%20skits%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20like%20a%20recent%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Theft%20Auto%26quot%3B%20spoof.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl