3Cli%3EToday%2C%20her%20three%20grown%20children%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20her%20ex-husband%20%E2%80%94%20are%20involved%20with%20the%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%20donated%20more%20than%20%2416%20million%20to%20charity%2C%20mostly%20for%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Lee%20Rhodes%2C%20founder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glassybaby.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlassybaby%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20youngest%20child%20was%20born%20in%201991%2C%20my%20chest%20would%20cramp%20in%20the%20oddest%20way%20when%20I%20was%20nursing%20him.%20I%20was%20only%2032%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-child-had-multiple-under-3-years-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20three%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20about%20three%20years%3B%20I%20figured%20my%20body%20had%20been%20through%20a%20lot.%20But%20my%20doctor%20sent%20me%20for%20an%20X-ray%2C%20then%20an%20MRI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20all%20three%20kids%20with%20me%2C%20lined%20up%20as%20I%20got%20into%20the%20MRI%20machine.%20The%20technician%20told%20me%20I'd%20be%20in%20the%20machine%20for%2070%20minutes%2C%20but%20she%20brought%20me%20out%20after%20only%20three%20minutes.%20She%20had%20tears%20streaming%20down%20her%20face%2C%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20must%20be%20a%20bigger%20emergency%20than%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20I%20was%20the%20emergency%3A%20I%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmulti-cancer-blood-test-does-grail-galleri-work-to-spot-cancer-early-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20tumor%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20right%20lung.%20That%20was%20a%20Friday%20afternoon%3B%20on%20Monday%2C%20I%20had%20surgery%20to%20remove%20part%20of%20my%20lung.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225870a585-096f-45bf-88c7-3bcd69f4ae72%5C%22%3EI%20found%20peace%20in%20a%20glass%20container%20my%20husband%20made%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20six-year%20battle%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnurse-short-of-breath-stage-four-lung-cancer-symptoms-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estage%204%20lung%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20did%20chemo%2C%20radiation%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20experimental%20treatments%20%E2%80%94%20which%20eventually%20worked.%20I'm%20one%20of%20the%20lucky%20ones%3A%20I've%20been%20cancer-free%20since%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20treatments%20while%20raising%20three%20young%20children%20was%20terrible.%20But%20I%20found%20solace%20in%20the%20most%20unexpected%20place%3A%20a%20glass%20votive%20my%20husband%20had%20made%20for%20me.%20When%20I%20dropped%20a%20candle%20into%20the%20container%2C%20I%20just%20stared%20at%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20light%20and%20flame.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20peace%2C%20just%20when%20I%20needed%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f5f62c3-c350-4435-8783-93ee43edc687%5C%22%3EI%20realized%20other%20patients%20didn't%20have%20the%20same%20resources%20I%20did%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20week%2C%20I%20would%20get%20chemotherapy%20alongside%20the%20same%20patients.%20We%20were%20like%20a%20band%20of%20brothers%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20we%20didn't%20all%20have%20the%20same%20means%20to%20take%20on%20this%20fight.%20I%20was%20bringing%20a%20beautiful%20whole-grain%20sandwich%20to%20eat%2C%20while%20other%20patients%20were%20grabbing%20Rice%20Krispies%20from%20the%20vending%20machine.%20I%20didn't%20think%20twice%20about%20paying%20%2416%20an%20hour%20for%20parking%2C%20while%20others%20missed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurvived-breast-cancer-wasnt-prepared-for-what-came-next-guilt-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echemo%20sessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20get%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20my%20basic%20needs%3A%20quality%20food%2C%20clean%20air%2C%20and%20good%20sleep.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20other%20patients%20couldn't%2C%20and%20the%20unfairness%20of%20that%20wore%20on%20me.%20It%20can%20still%20make%20me%20cry%2C%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20thinking%20about%20how%20to%20connect%20the%20peace%20I%20felt%20from%20my%20glass%20votive%20while%20helping%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feven-with-insurance-my-breast-cancer-treatment-was-expensive-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancer%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20didn't%20have%20the%20same%20financial%20means%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293d9cfee-82d4-43dc-9b76-8c02c0d6a1f3%5C%22%3EA%20connection%20to%20Martha%20Stewart%20boosted%20sales%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sold%20the%20first%20Glassybaby%20votives%20on%20Breast%20Cancer%20Awareness%20Day%20in%201996%2C%20right%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20the%20hospital.%20Before%20cancer%2C%20I%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-career-stay-at-home-mom-guilt-identity-money-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay-at-home%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20about%20this%20as%20a%20business%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20fundraiser.%20I%20connected%20with%20local%20artisans%20to%20purchase%20their%20glasswork%2C%20and%20donated%20all%20of%20the%20profits%20to%20uncompensated%20care%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20pretty%20informally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20people%20heard%20about%20the%20glass%2C%20demand%20grew%3A%20loved%20ones%20of%20patients%20began%20buying%20multiple%20Glassybabies%20and%20lighting%20them%20at%20the%20same%20time%20to%20send%20healing%20to%20their%20loved%20ones.%20The%20impact%20of%20flame%20and%20color%20was%20so%20meaningful.%20At%20the%20very%20least%2C%20I%20feel%20as%20though%20it%20reminds%20you%20to%20be%20a%20better%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20three%20years%2C%20I%20realized%20Glassybaby%20had%20real%20business%20potential.%20By%202003%2C%20I%20had%20opened%20my%20own%20store%20near%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-nyc-to-seattle-only-lasted-one-year-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20in%20Washington%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20I%20brought%20the%20votives%20to%20a%20friend's%20party%20%E2%80%94%20a%20party%20that%20Martha%20Stewart's%20boyfriend%20was%20attending.%20He%20loved%20the%20Glassybabies%2C%20and%20brought%20them%20home%20to%20Martha%2C%20which%20is%20how%20I%20ended%20up%20on%20her%20show.%20That's%20when%20sales%20really%20blew%20up.%20I%20still%20remember%20the%20stacks%20and%20stacks%20of%20paper%20order%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223542369f-b5ca-43e9-b728-d10dca72c535%5C%22%3EMy%20grown%20kids%20are%20still%20involved%20with%20the%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Glassybaby%20did%20over%20%2427%20million%20in%20sales.%20As%20I%20grew%20the%20business%20has%20grown%2C%20I've%20kept%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-focused-on-ethics-do-better-mcgowan-director-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eethos%20of%20giving%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%20How%20we%20do%20that%20has%20evolved%20over%20time%3A%20at%20one%20point%2C%20we%20donated%20a%20set%20percentage%20of%20profits%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20donate%20%243%20for%20every%20Glassybaby%20we%20sell.%20We've%20donated%20more%20than%20%2416%20million%20to%20charities%20through%20our%20foundation%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202015.%20This%20little%20candle%20holder%20really%20does%20good%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20my%20kids%20are%20in%20their%2030s%2C%20and%20they're%20all%20involved%20with%20the%20business%20in%20some%20way.%20Even%20my%20now%20ex-husband%20helps%20with%20design%20occasionally%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20I've%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorced-after-husband-came-out-new-family-dynamics-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappily%20divorced%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20remarried%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20grew%20up%20with%20this%20company%2C%20and%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20Glassybaby%20feels%20like%20their%20sibling%2C%20and%20my%20fourth%20child.%20The%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20donations%20it%20facilitates%20%E2%80%94%20have%20given%20our%20lives%20meaning.%20It%20means%20the%20world%20to%20me%20that%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20work%20together%20to%20create%20something%20that's%20bigger%20than%20any%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-started-company-while-battling-stage-4-lung-cancer-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780484821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1da3a3b4fb977f35982c9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-started-company-while-battling-stage-4-lung-cancer-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lee%20Rhodes%20started%20her%20company%2C%20Glassybaby%2C%20as%20a%20mom%20of%20three%20with%20stage%204%20lung%20cancer.%20Her%20kids%20are%20now%20all%20adults%20and%20involved%20in%20the%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Henry%20Nowak%20murder%20protest%20turns%20violent%3A%2011%20police%20officers%20injured%2C%202%20arrested%20in%20Southampton%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780484766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131482584%2Cimgsize-76422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fhenry-nowak-murder-protest-turns-v