-approves-rs-10-000-crore-fund-to-stabilise-atf-costs-amid-crisis-126060300783_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Graduates%20are%20coming%20into%20the%20workforce%20thinking%20that%20using%20AI%20is%20cheating%2C%20a%20top%20Deloitte%20exec%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227214%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deloitte%20logo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1fe0e82e5a80cfe0502a53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20use%20is%20a%20key%20competency%20in%20consulting%2C%20but%20many%20graduates%20are%20coming%20into%20the%20workforce%20thinking%20that%20using%20it%20is%20wrong.%3Cp%3EMatthias%20Balk%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20top%20Deloitte%20executive%20says%20colleges%20are%20not%20preparing%20students%20for%20the%20AI-centric%20workplace.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20developing%20a%20negative%20perception%20and%20teaching%20students%20that%20using%20AI%20is%20cheating%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20Gallup%20poll%20found%20that%2042%25%20of%20US%20colleges%20discourage%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20schoolwork.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EColleges%20are%20failing%20to%20prepare%20students%20for%20an%20AI-driven%20workplace%20by%20teaching%20many%20of%20them%20to%20treat%20the%20technology%20as%20cheating%2C%20according%20to%20Rob%20Hillard%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Deloitte's%20Asia-Pacific%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20future%20of%20work%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20this%20week%2C%20Hillard%20said%20recent%20graduates%20were%20entering%20the%20workforce%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bnegative%20perception%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20after%20being%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-students-use-ai-homework-study-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaught%20in%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20it%C2%A0is%20used%20for%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20many%20are%20seeing%20the%20technology%20as%20cheating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20change%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Deloitte%20executive%20said%20universities%20have%20been%20slow%20to%20make%20AI%20a%20central%20part%20of%20how%20students%20prepare%20for%20the%20workplace%2C%20and%20added%20that%20changing%20these%20perceptions%20of%20the%20technology%20is%20key%20to%20successfully%20evolving%20the%20workplace%20as%20AI%20evolves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20invent%20and%20design%20the%20work%20of%20the%20future%20is%20by%20%26quot%3Bworking%20hands-on%20with%20the%20technology%2C%20with%20seeing%20how%20you%20can%20get%20the%20most%20effective%20interface%20between%20people%20and%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20Hillard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20survey%20from%20Gallup%20and%20the%20Lumina%20Foundation%20of%20around%203%2C800%20students%20found%20that%2042%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20their%20school%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-changing-majors-because-of-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediscourages%20the%20use%20of%20AI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2011%25%20said%20the%20technology%20is%20prohibited%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20reluctance%20among%20educators%20is%20partly%20driven%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flecturer-ai-cheating-students-chatgpt-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efears%20of%20cheating%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20by%C2%A0attempts%20to%20encourage%20independent%2C%20critical%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20reporting%20restrictions%20on%20AI%20use%2C%20more%20than%20half%20%E2%80%94%2057%25%20%E2%80%94%20of%20US%20college%20students%20said%20they%20use%20AI%20in%20their%20coursework%20at%20least%20weekly%2C%20and%20one%20in%20five%20said%20they%20use%20it%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20use%20in%20colleges%20has%20come%20into%20sharp%20focus%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20with%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-commencement-speeches-graduation-reactions-class-of-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egraduation%20speakers%20being%20booed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20students%20when%20mentioning%20the%20tech's%20growing%20role%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239274ad6-d7f8-43c5-bab1-bf04159fd0ad%5C%22%3EConsulting's%20AI%20anxiety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20around%20AI-driven%20job%20displacement%20is%20particularly%20acute%20in%20the%20professional%20services%20industry.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20firms%2C%20including%20Deloitte%2C%20are%20racing%20to%20embed%20generative%20and%20agentic%20AI%20into%20their%20workflows%2C%20using%20the%20new%20technology%20to%20expedite%20repetitive%2C%20data-heavy%20tasks%20that%20were%20previously%20left%20to%20junior%20workers.%20That%20shift%20is%20creating%20questions%20about%20the%20firms'%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-ai-agents-creating-upskilling-challenge-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeducation%20strategies%20for%20upskilling%3C%2Fa%3E%20junior%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20for%20certain%20job%20roles%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-industry-outlook-management-consultants-ai-hiring-job-cuts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emanagement%20consultants%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20down%2C%20and%20Deloitte's%20fellow%20Big%20Four%20firm%20PwC%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-hiring-fewer-junior-associates-ai-offshoring-big-four-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecut%20all%20entry-level%20recruitment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20by%20a%20third%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20impact%20of%20AI%26quot%3B%2C%20Business%20Insider%20exclusively%20re