3A%20Look%20at%20small%20businesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Cuban%20in%20the%20South%20Court%20Auditorium%20of%20the%20Eisenhower%20Executive%20Office%20Building%20at%20the%20White%20House%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20US%2C%20on%20May%2018%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1ff1512e5a80cfe0502a7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBillionaire%20entrepreneur%20Mark%20Cuban.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Cuban%20advised%20job%20seekers%20to%20look%20at%20small%20businesses%20in%20their%20search.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20pushed%20back%20on%20concerns%20that%20AI%20would%20reduce%20hiring%20at%20these%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20the%20help.%20Kids%20coming%20out%20of%20college%20have%20that%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20AI%20skills.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20reshapes%20the%20job%20market%2C%20Mark%20Cuban%20has%20a%20simple%20piece%20of%20career%20advice%3A%20look%20at%20small%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ask-5-questions-company-leadership-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillionaire%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20small%20businesses%20create%20about%2060%25%20of%20new%20jobs%20each%20year%20and%20that%20AI%20will%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Beasier%20and%20faster%26quot%3B%20for%20them%20to%20compete%20with%20larger%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20firms%20with%20fewer%20than%20250%20employees%20accounted%20for%2051%25%20of%20net%20job%20creation%20between%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202020%20and%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%25%20of%20jobs%20created%20by%20Small%20biz%20every%20year%20will%20only%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BStart%20your%20job%20search%20with%20small%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban's%20comments%20come%20as%20employers%20grapple%20with%20how%20AI%20will%20affect%20hiring.%20Some%20companies%20have%20cited%20the%20technology%20to%20automate%20tasks%20and%20trim%20head%20count%2C%20while%20others%20say%20it%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-ai-jobs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreate%20new%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20make%20workers%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20X%20user%20questioned%20whether%20AI%20would%20actually%20lead%20to%20more%20hiring%2C%20saying%20startups%20may%20become%20leaner%20and%20employ%20fewer%20people%2C%20Cuban%20said%20smaller%20companies%20still%20need%20help%20using%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20smallest%20businesses%20don't%20have%20the%20depth%20of%20expertise%20in%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThey%20need%20the%20help.%20Kids%20coming%20out%20of%20college%20have%20that%20expertise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20also%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20idea%20that%20small%20businesses%20would%20mainly%20use%20AI%20to%20cut%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20response%20to%20another%20user.%20%26quot%3BThey%20use%20it%20to%20do%20things%20they%20didn't%20have%20enough%20time%20to%20do%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban's%20comments%20echo%20advice%20he%20gave%20to%20new%20graduates%20in%20December.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20said%20recent%20grads%20should%20consider%20joining%20small%20and%20midsize%20businesses%20because%20they%20could%20help%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-new-grads-small-businesses-ai-agents-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadopt%20AI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20automate%20processes%20they%20previously%20lacked%20the%20time%20or%20budget%20to%20handle%20manually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBig%20companies%20don't%20need%20new%20grads%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20wrote%20on%20X%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BEntrepreneurial%20companies%20will%20love%20the%20value%20you%20add.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-era-job-advice-look-at-small-businesses-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780480808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1ff1c02e5a80cfe0502a80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-era-job-advice-look-at-small-businesses-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStart%20your%20job%20search%20with%20small%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Billionaire%20Mark%20Cuban%20tells%20job%20seekers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brooklinen%20Luxe%20Sateen%20Sheets%202.0%20review%3A%20I%20tested%20the%20bedding%20upgrade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20brooklinen%20sheets%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f4be02e5a80cfe050295c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrooklinen%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20year%20revamping%20it's%20assortment%2C%20now%20it's%20best-selling%20Luxe%20Sateen%20Sheets%20get%20a%20refresh.%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%20has%20dominated%20the%20bedding%20landscape%20with%20high-quality%20bedroom%20basics%20for%20the%20last%2012%20years.%20Over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20focused%20on%20updating%20its%20assortment%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20better%20materials%20and%20durability.%20First%2C%20they%20revamped%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklinen-linen-bed-sheets-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclassic%20linen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20overhauled%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklinen-down-pillow-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edown%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improved%20the%20signature%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bath-towels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplush%20bath%20towels%20and%20robes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20it's%20time%20for%20the%20brand's%20flagship%20product%20and%20my%20Brooklinen%20holy%20grail%20to%20get%20the%20upgrade%20treatment%3A%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D8014f9da9cdbfcaf0bf35a1b6381b772b7ab593e04e8ec5efc01cc4fed4790f1%26postID%3D6a1ee040ece48d21e3fa1aaa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbrooklinen-luxe-sateen-sheets-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fluxe-core-sheet-set%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELuxe%20Sateen%20Sheets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Having%20tested%20dozens%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sheets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20is%20the%20exact%20set%20I've%20turned%20to%20time%20and%20time%20again%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%20is%20describing%20its%20new%20Sateen%202.0%20as%20%26quot%3Bluxier.%26quot%3B%20As%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20original%2C%20I%20didn't%20necessarily%20think%20the%20OG%20set%20needed%20revamping%2C%20but%20Brooklinen%20says%20it%20spent%20three%20years%20considering%20customer%20feedback%20and%20fabric%20research%20to%20reimagine%20its%20sheets.%20After%20two%20weeks%20of%20trying%20the%20new%20sheets%2C%20I'll%20definitely%20be%20keeping%20them%20in%20my%20bedding%20rotation.%20They%20retain%20the%20same%20signature%20cozy%20softness%2C%20with%20subtle%20construction%20upgrades%20designed%20to%20enhance%20breathability%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelated%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklinen-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOur%20favorite%20products%20we've%20tested%20from%20Brooklinen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c20e25c-b7c2-4071-afe5-97774b7d4664%5C%22%3EHere's%20what's%20different%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20sheets%20on%20a%20bed%20and%20the%20new%20b%20tag%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f04182ab5f9757add80fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrooklinen%20added%20a%20lowercase%20%26quot%3Bb%26quot%3B%20tag%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20flat%20sheet.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20talk%20specs%3A%20the%20new%20Luxe%20Sateen%20Sheets%20are%20produced%20and%20sewn%20in%20Portugal.%20Brooklinen%20says%20the%20finer%20long-staple%20cotton%20and%20slightly%20higher%20thread%20count%20are%20meant%20to%20improve%20softness%2C%20durability%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20drape.%20In%20practice%2C%20the%20differences%20are%20subtle%3A%20the%20new%20sheets%20feel%20a%20little%20thicker%20and%20smoother%2C%20but%20not%20dramatically%20different%20from%20the%20original%20Luxe%20Sateen%20set%2C%20which%20also%20used%20long-staple%20cotton%20fibers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%20increased%20the%20thread%20count%20to%20495%20from%20480.%20This%20subtle%20change%20makes%20the%20sheets%20more%20durable%2C%20and%20less%20sheer.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20unspecified%20finish%20that%20reduces%20sheen.%20I%20didn't%20quite%20notice%20this%20change%2C%20but%20sateen%20is%20typically%20regarded%20as%20shinier%20when%20compared%20to%20coarser%20weaves%20like%20percale.%20Brooklinen%20added%20a%20%26quot%3BB%26quot%3B%20logo%20tag%20to%20the%20side%20edge%20of%20the%20flat%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20launch%2C%20the%20sheets%20are%20available%20in%2016%20evergreen%20colorways%2C%20echoing%20the%20same%20colors%20these%20sheets%20replace%2C%20plus%20seven%20seasonal%20colors%20including%20stripes%20and%20florals.%20The%20sheets%20continue%20to%20be%20offered%20in%20the%20classic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D8014f9da9cdbfcaf0bf35a1b6381b772b7ab593e04e8ec5efc01cc4fed4790f1%26postID%3D6a1ee040ece48d21e3fa1aaa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbrooklinen-luxe-sateen-sheets-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fluxe-core-sheet-set%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECore%20Sheet%20Set%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20your%20standard%204-piece%20set%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D0f5f52862a9722510864cc0528a140c50635cf1eabdcca85d0e60d941410fb19%26postID%3D6a1ee040ece48d21e3fa1aaa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbrooklinen-luxe-sateen-sheets-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fluxe-hardcore-sheet-bundle%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHardcore%20Sheet%20Bundle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20sheet%20set%2C%20plus%20a%20duvet%20cover%20and%20extra%20pillow%20cases%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20individually%20and%20other%20sets.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20not%20without%20a%20small%20price%20increase%20of%20about%20%2410%2C%20with%20the%20Core%20set%20now%20starting%20at%20%24229%20for%20a%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1a79ac5-cc92-4e6b-81cb-d865ba5e00b1%5C%22%3EWhat's%20the%20same%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22short%20and%20long%20care%20tags%20and%20pillowcases%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f0418b4fb977f35983570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrooklinen's%20signature%20long%20and%20short%20side%20tags%20as%20remain%2C%20as%20does%20the%20envelope%20style%20pillowcases%2C%20just%20with%20a%20subtly%20different%20trim.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Long%20and%20Short%20side%20tags%20that%20make%20for%20easier%20and%20faster%20bed-making%20and%20that%20are%20a%20staple%20of%20Brooklinen's%20construction%20remain.%20The%20pillowcases%20still%20have%20envelope%20closures%2C%20though%20I%20noticed%20the%20back%20stitching%20to%20have%20a%20slightly%20larger%20trim%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen's%20sheets%20are%20still%20OEKO-TEX%C2%AE%20STANDARD%20100%20certified%2C%20an%20independent%20certification%20that%20proves%20has%20been%20rigorously%20tested%20and%20deemed%20safe%20from%20over%201%2C000%20harmful%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheets%20still%20fit%20mattresses%20up%20to%2016%20inches%20thick.%20The%20elasticized%20fitted%20sheet%20holds%20snug%20to%20the%20bed%20and%20didn't%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a981aaae-436c-4150-987f-8c4b069c81d4%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Luxe%20Sateen%20sheets%20feel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Luxe%20Sateen%20sheets%20retain%20their%20smooth%20and%20buttery%20luster%20that%20is%20characteristic%20of%20sateen%20sheets.%20They're%20Brooklinen's%20softest%20option%2C%20best%20suited%20for%20those%20looking%20for%20year-round%20cozy%20comfort.%20The%20material%20also%20feels%20slightly%20thicker%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20comparing%20to%20a%20sheet%20set%20going%20on%20six%20years%20and%20countless%20wash%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20breathable%2C%20to%20the%20degree%20that%20I%20didn't%20feel%20myself%20kicking%20off%20the%20sheets%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20but%20if%20you%20are%20extremely%20temperature%20sensitive%2C%20I%20suggest%20exploring%20Brooklinen's%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-sheets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecooling%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%20options%2C%20like%20linen%20or%20percale.%20Brooklinen's%20percale%20a%20crisp%2C%20airy%20feel%2C%20while%20the%20washed%20linen%20has%20a%20more%20relaxed%2C%20slightly%20textured%20feel%20with%20unmatched%20temperature%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20need%20more%20time%20and%20repeated%20wash%20cycles%20to%20fully%20assess%20Brooklinen's%20durability%20claims%2C%20but%20after%20the%20first%20wash%2C%20I%20didn't%20notice%20shrinkage%2C%20pilling%2C%20or%20a%20change%20in%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266f06b69-f5ab-493c-8e53-b55b6c17cf18%5C%22%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20love%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20change%20with%20these%20sheets%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20see%20from%20Brookline%20is%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20fabric%20sleeve%20rather%20than%20the%20plastic%20wrapping%20these%20sheets%20come%20in.%20Not%20only%20would%20it%20add%20a%20more%20luxurious%20element%20to%20unboxing%2C%20but%20they're%20practical%20to%20store%20bedding%20in%20and%20also%20directly%20compare%20how%20quality%20enhances%20(or%20deteriorates)%20from%20use%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20with%20this%20launch%2C%20while%20Brooklinen%20maintains%20its%20core%20color%20palette%20of%20creams%2C%20taupes%2C%20and%20blues%2C%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20see%20more%20integration%20of%20colors%2C%20like%20pink%20or%20purple%2C%20and%20even%20grey.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20similar%20shades%2C%20mostly%20designed%20for%20easy%20mixing%20and%20matching%2C%20but%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20more%20shade%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22849ec56b-464d-484b-b4b6-1d793d76a170%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20dog%20snoozes%20on%20a%20pillow%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f02fd2e5a80cfe05025e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20very%20snoozy%20pup%20sleeping%20deep%20on%20his%20Brooklinen%20sheets.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D8014f9da9cdbfcaf0bf35a1b6381b772b7ab593e04e8ec5efc01cc4fed4790f1%26postID%3D6a1ee040ece48d21e3fa1aaa%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbrooklinen-luxe-sateen-sheets-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.brooklinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fluxe-core-sheet-set%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrooklinen's%20Luxe%20Sateen%202.0%3C%2Fa%3E%20builds%20on%20the%20brand's%20commitment%20to%20quality%20and%20durability.%20If%20you're%20actively%20looking%20to%20refresh%20your%20bedding%2C%20add%20a%20second%20set%2C%20or%20have%20fun%20with%20the%20seasonal%20colorways%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20wrong%20with%20upgrading%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20this%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20where%2C%20if%20you%20already%20own%20and%20love%20the%20Luxe%20Sateen%20Set%2C%20you%20may%20not%20notice%20a%20dramatic%20side-by-side%20difference.%20The%20updates%20are%20incremental%2C%20but%20they%20make%20an%20already%20great%20sheet%20set%20feel%20just%20a%20little%20more%20refined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuy%20if%20%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyou%20want%20soft%2C%20smooth%2C%20slightly%20weightier%20sheets%20and%20like%20a%20polished%20sateen%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkip%20if%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyou%20sleep%20very%20hot%2C%20prefer%20crisp%20sheets%2C%20already%20own%20Luxe%20Sateen%20in%20good%20condition%2C%