s%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fscience%2Fwhat-keeps-the-grand-canyon-alive-scientists-reveal-a-hidden-underground-system-beneath-one-of-earths-greatest-wonders%2Famp_articleshow%2F131481035.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ram%20Charan's%20'Peddi'%20mints%20over%20Rs%2011%20crore%20in%20advance%20bookings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780479542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131481028%2Cimgsize-126172.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fpeddi-mints-over-rs-11-crore-in-advance-bookings-ram-charans-pan-indian-film-set-for-massive-opening%2Farticleshow%2F131481012.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131481012.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERam%20Charan's%20pan-Indian%20film%20'Peddi'%20has%20garnered%20over%20Rs%2011%20crore%20in%20advance%20bookings%2C%20with%20Rs%206.61%20crore%20from%20domestic%20ticket%20sales%20and%20Rs%207.6%20crore%20from%20overseas%20markets.%20The%20rural%20sports%20drama%2C%20directed%20by%20Buchi%20Babu%20Sana%2C%20is%20poised%20for%20a%20massive%20opening%20on%20June%204%2C%20fueled%20by%20strong%20audience%20interest%20and%20the%20actor's%20growing%20global%20popularity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20millennial%20who%20saved%20up%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20stressful%20job%20says%20he%20found%20'the%20cheat%20code'%20to%20hitting%20FIRE%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223731%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andy%20hill%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f0cb22ab5f9757add8166%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndy%20Hill%20left%20corporate%20America%20in%202020%20to%20build%20his%20content%20creation%20and%20coaching%20business%2C%20Marriage%20Kids%20and%20Money.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andy%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Hill%20says%20the%20%26quot%3Bcheat%20code%20for%20the%20FIRE%20movement%26quot%3B%20is%20twofold.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20involves%20hitting%20Coast%20FIRE%20and%20building%20an%20FU%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20two-part%20strategy%20allowed%20Hill%20and%20his%20wife%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20corporate%20jobs%20and%20pursue%20different%20careers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FIRE%20movement%E2%80%94shorthand%20for%20financial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early%E2%80%94emphasizes%20aggressive%20saving%20and%20strategic%20investing%20to%20build%20a%20nest%20egg%20large%20enough%20to%20stop%20working%20well%20before%20the%20traditional%20retirement%20age.%20Oftentimes%2C%20participants%20save%20more%20than%20half%20their%20income%20to%20build%20seven-figure%20portfolios%20that%20will%20sustain%20them%20in%20early%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Hill%2C%20a%20family%20finance%20coach%20who%20pursued%20traditional%20FIRE%20before%20pivoting%20to%20a%20more%20flexible%20version%20of%20the%20movement%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-fire-vs-coast-fire-financial-independence-retire-early-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoast%20FIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20doesn't%20think%20everyone%20needs%20to%20accumulate%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20achieve%20financial%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20simpler%2C%20more%20sustainable%20path%2C%20the%2044-year-old%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BCoast%20FIRE%2C%20combined%20with%20FU%20money%2C%20is%20the%20cheat%20code%20for%20the%20FIRE%20movement.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoast%20FIRE%20still%20involves%20front-loading%20your%20investments%2C%20but%20the%20goal%20isn't%20to%20stop%20working%20altogether.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20to%20a%20point%20where%20you%20can%20stop%20contributing%20to%20your%20nest%20egg%20and%20%26quot%3Bcoast%26quot%3B%20into%20retirement.%20You%20can%20then%20redirect%20that%20money%20toward%20other%20priorities%2C%20whether%20that's%20spending%20more%20on%20experiences%2C%20working%20fewer%20hours%2C%20changing%20careers%2C%20or%20starting%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill's%20Coast%20FIRE%20number%20was%20about%20%24550%2C000%20invested%20by%20age%2040.%20Assuming%20a%206%25%20annual%20rate%20of%20return%2C%20that%20balance%20could%20grow%20to%20roughly%20%242%20million%20by%20retirement%20age%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bplenty%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on.%26quot%3B%20Had%20he%20been%20pursuing%20traditional%20FIRE%2C%20his%20target%20would%20have%20been%20significantly%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20Hill's%20cheat%20code%20is%20%26quot%3BFU%20money%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20cash%20cushion%20that%20gives%20you%20the%20confidence%20and%20freedom%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20job%20or%20situation%20that%20no%20longer%20aligns%20with%20your%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%2C%20who%20felt%20trapped%20in%20a%20stressful%20corporate%20marketing%20job%2C%20determined%20he%20needed%2012%20months'%20worth%20of%20living%20expenses%20in%20his%20FU%20fund%20before%20he%20would%20feel%20comfortable%20leaving%20behind%20a%20steady%20paycheck%20and%20trying%20something%20more%20entrepreneurial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andy%20hill%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f0d202e5a80cfe050266c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHill%20interviews%20young%20millionaires%2C%20financially%20independent%20couples%2C%20and%20debt-free%20parents%20on%20his%20podcast.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andy%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Nicole%2C%20reached%20both%20their%20Coast%20FIRE%20number%20and%20their%20FU%20fund%20goal.%20It%20allowed%20Hill%20to%20leave%20corporate%20America%20and%20focus%20on%20turning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarriagekidsandmoney.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarriage%20Kids%20and%20Money%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20blog%20and%20podcast%20he%20started%20as%20a%20side%20project%20in%202016%20%E2%80%94%20into%20a%20full-time%20business.%20Nicole%20also%20left%20her%20corporate%20job%20and%20attended%20trade%20school%20to%20become%20an%20aesthetician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20views%20FU%20money%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20where%20you%20are%20and%20where%20you'd%20like%20to%20be%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20you%20walk%20into%20a%20life%20that%20you%20are%20excited%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275a6c4bd-8231-4313-b689-9dc5fca18a9e%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20build%20your%20%26quot%3BFU%20fund%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20recommends%20keeping%20FU%20money%20in%20a%20high-yield%20savings%20account%2C%20where%20it%20remains%20accessible%20while%20earning%20a%20higher%20return%20than%20a%20traditional%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20building%20that%20warchest%20is%20knowing%20where%20your%20money%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnderstanding%20our%20expenses%20was%20super%20key%20to%20understanding%20what%20we%20actually%20needed%20to%20live%20on%20and%20what%20was%20realistic%20for%20Coast%20FIRE%20and%20FU%20money%20calculations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20To%20stay%20on%20track%2C%20Hill%20and%20his%20wife%20held%20monthly%20money%20meetings%20to%20review%20their%20spending%2C%20discuss%20upcoming%20expenses%2C%20and%20evaluate%20their%20progress%20toward%20shared%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20extremely%20revealing%20when%20you%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20and%20say%2C%20'Does%20this%20really%20align%20with%20where%20I%20want%20to%20go%20in%20life%20or%20our%20family%20values%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20it%20doesn't%2C%20it's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20eliminate%2C%20modify%2C%20or%20change%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20for%20savings%20opportunities%2C%20Hill%20recommends%20focusing%20on%20the%20biggest%20spending%20categories%20first%3A%20housing%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bigger%20expenses%20matter%20the%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20some%20of%20the%20harder%20questions%20to%20ask%20yourself%3A%20Do%20I%20actually%20need%20this%20house%3F%20Do%20I%20need%20these%20cars%3F%20Are%20they%20helping%20me%20get%20where%20I%20want%20to%20go%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cautions%20against%20treating%20financial%20independence%20as%20a%20game%20of%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20be%20about%20finding%20the%20cheapest%20option.%20It%20can't%20be%20about%20what's%20the%20most%20frugal%20hack%20here%2C%20because%20you%20need%20to%20also%20consider%20life%20enjoyment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20look%20at%20the%20expenses%20that%20don't%20kill%20your%20joy%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20income%20is%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20equation%2C%20especially%20in%20today's%20inflationary%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20combat%20inflation%20by%20inflating%20our%20own%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20with%20your%20current%20job%3A%20Can%20you%20ask%20for%20a%20raise%2C%20go%20for%20a%20promotion%2C%20or%20work%20overtime%3F%20Next%2C%20consider%20a%20side%20hustle%20that%20leverages%20an%20existing%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20through%20spending%20cuts%2C%20higher%20earnings%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20enough%20financial%20breathing%20room%20to%20build%20a%20cash%20cushion%20that%20expands%20your%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFU%20money%20allows%20you%20to%20move%20toward%20something%20that's%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-fire-advice-tips-fu-money-early-retirement-financial-independence-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780479302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f0cc72ab5f9757add8167%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-fire-advice-tips-fu-money-early-retirement-financial-independence-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andy%20Hill%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20in%202020%2C%20says%20you%20don't%20need%20as%20much%20as%20you%20think%20to%20be%20financially%20independent.%20Here's%20his%20advice%20for%20FIRE%20seekers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2267%2C800-year-old%20cave%20art%20in%20Indonesia%20recognised%20by%20Guinness%20World%20Records%20reveals%20human%20evolution%20history%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780479242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131480946%2Cimgsize-92944.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F67800-year-old-cave-art-in-indonesia-recognised-by-guinness-world-records-reveals-human-evolution-history%2Farticleshow%2F131479594.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131479594.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F67800-year-old-cave-art-in-indonesia-recognised-by-guinness-world-records-reveals-human-evolution-history%2Farticleshow%2F131479594.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F67800-year-old-cave-art-in-indonesia-recognised-by-guinness-world-records-reveals-human-evolution-history%2Famp_articleshow%2F131479594.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2F67800-year-old-cave-art-in-indonesia-recognised-by-guinness-world-records-reveals-human-evolution-history%2Famp_articleshow%2F131479594.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20to%20cut%20taxes%2C%20relax%20bond%20ownership%20rules%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780479099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-06%2F03%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1780479012-6393.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-cut-taxes-relax-bond-ownership-rules-to-attract-foreign-investment-126060300719_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cabinet%20on%20Wednesday%20is%20expected%20to%20consider%20a%20significant%20cut%20in%20the%20taxes%20paid%20by%20global%20funds%20on%20the%20nation's%20bonds%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-cut-taxes-relax-bond-ownership-rules-to-attract-foreign-investment-126060300719_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-cut-taxes-relax-bond-ownership-rules-to-attract-foreign-investment-126060300719_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-cut-taxes-relax-bond-ownership-rules-to-attract-foreign-investment-126060300719_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20ex-lawyer%20has%20raised%20%2470%20million%20from%20VCs%20to%20take%20work%20away%20from%20law%20firms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20with%20glasses%20sits%20at%20a%20restaurant%20table%20with%20a%20coffee%20mug%20in%20front%20of%20him.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f1a5d2ab5f9757add81d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoss%20McNairn.%3Cp%3EOhad%20Kab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELegal%20tech%20startup%20Wordsmith%20has%20raised%20%2470%20million%20in%20new%20funding%20to%20fuel%20expansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20develops%20software%20to%20help%20corporate%20legal%20teams%20automate%20drafting%20and%20other%20tasks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWordsmith%20is%20part%20of%20a%20wave%20of%20legal%20tech%20startups%20focused%20on%20corporate%20legal%20services%20instead%20of%20law%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20promise%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20law%20is%20not%20that%20lawyers%20will%20work%20faster.%20It's%20that%20companies%20will%20need%20fewer%20of%20them%20on%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWordsmith%2C%20a%20startup%20built%20around%20that%20bet%2C%20has%20raised%20%2470%20million%20in%20new%20funding%20to%20help%20corporate%20legal%20teams%20bring%20more%20work%20in-house%20and%20send%20less%20of%20it%20to%20law%20firms.%20The%20round%2C%20backed%20by%20Index%20Ventures%2C%20Highland%20Europe%2C%20and%20others%2C%20brings%20the%20company's%20total%20funding%20to%20%24100%20million%2C%20which%20was%20raised%20in%2024%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20makes%20software%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-house-legal-tech-ai-cost-cutting-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein-house%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20run%20their%20department.%20Wordsmith%20pulls%20in%20requests%20from%20tools%20like%20email%2C%20Slack%2C%20Microsoft%20Teams%2C%20and%20Salesforce%2C%20takes%20a%20first%20pass%20at%20drafting%20contracts%20and%20answering%20legal%20questions%2C%20and%20routes%20each%20matter%20to%20the%20right%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20has%20grown%20from%20the%20company's%20founding%20days%20in%20Edinburgh%2C%20Scotland%2C%20said%20Ross%20McNairn%2C%20Wordsmith's%20founder%20and%20chief%20executive.%20Today%2C%20its%20software%20is%20used%20by%20more%20than%20500%20companies%2C%20including%20legal%20teams%20at%20Canva%2C%20Financial%20Times%2C%20Safelite%2C%20Trip.com%2C%20and%20BT%2C%20a%20major%20British%20telecom%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20days%20of%20the%20legal%20artificial%20intelligence%20boom%20were%20defined%20by%20startups%20selling%20to%20law%20firms.%20Billions%20of%20dollars%20were%20poured%20into%20Harvey%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flegora-founder-harvey-legal-tech-ai-platform-competition-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELegora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20others%2C%20promising%20to%20make%20firms%20faster%20and%20more%20profitable.%20Some%20of%20those%20same%20companies%20have%20since%20expanded%20into%20corporate%20legal%20departments%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharvey-ceo-ai-agents-transforming-legal-industry-dynamics-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHarvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20saying%20in-house%20customers%20account%20for%2040%25%20of%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20trying%20to%20play%20both%20sides%2C%20Wordsmith%20has%20chosen%20one%3A%20the%20companies%20trying%20to%20send%20less%20work%20to%20law%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcNairn's%20argument%20is%20that%20a%20software%20company%20cannot%20credibly%20tell%20law%20firms%20it%20will%20help%20them%20become%20more%20profitable%20while%20also%20telling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsynthesia-general-counsel-vibe-coding-ai-lawyer-legal-agent-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20legal%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20will%20help%20them%20rely%20less%20on%20those%20same%20firms.%20He%20said%20Wordsmith%20courted%20law%20firms%20in%20its%20early%20days%2C%20but%20later%20walked%20away%20from%20potential%20seven-figure%20contracts%20because%20he%20thought%20serving%20both%20sides%20created%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20really%20in%20good%20conscience%20serve%20the%20people%20that%20I'm%20diminishing%20the%20business%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcNairn%2C%20a%20trained%20lawyer%2C%20left%20the%20practice%20after%20deciding%20that%20software%20could%20scale%20in%20ways%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcleary-gottlieb-lawyer-michael-gerstenzang-on-billable-hour-model-ai-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elegal%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20not.%20He%20spent%20the%20next%20decade%20in%20tech%2C%20building%20and%20scaling%20startups%20in%20the%20travel%20sector.%20He%20sold%20his%20first%20startup%2C%20Dorsai%20Travel%2C%20to%20Skyscanner%20in%202014%2C%20then%20held%20senior%20roles%20at%20Skyscanner%20and%20TravelPerk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20McNairn%20arrived%20at%20OpenAI's%20office%20for%20an%20early%20look%20at%20its%20technology%2C%20by%20invitation%20of%20an%20investor%2C%20General%20Catalyst.%20Afterward%2C%20he%20started%20building%20tools%20with%20OpenAI's%20large%20language%20model%20inside%20TravelPerk.%20One%20early%20project%20helped%20triage%20an%20inbox%20full%20of%20travel%20changes%20and%20cancellations%20%E2%80%94%20work%20that%20previously%20required%20a%20team%20of%20people%20to%20sort%2C%20match%20to%20trips%2C%20and%20update%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20took%20the%20queue%20down%20to%20zero%20overnight%2C%20McNairn%20said.%20It%20offered%20a%20window%20into%20what%20would%20become%20possible%20with%20the%20new%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20McNairn%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20began%20dreaming%20up%20what%20would%20become%20Wordsmith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndex%20Ventures%2C%20whose%20early%20bets%20include%20Figma%2C%20Dropbox%2C%20and%20Slack%2C%20caught%20wind%20that%20McNairn%20was%20starting%20something%20new.%20Before%20he%20had%20fully%20left%20TravelPerk%2C%20he%20had%20a%20term%20sheet%20to%20fund%20the%20next%20company.%20Index%20has%20invested%20in%20every%20round%20since%2C%20McNairn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20looked%20like%20a%20narrow%20market%20when%20Wordsmith%20started%20has%20quickly%20become%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20corners%20of%20legal%20tech.%20One%20of%20the%20furthest%20along%20is%20GC%20AI%2C%20which%20said%20it%20raised%20%2460%20million%20last%20year%20after%20growing%20annualized%20revenue%20from%20%241%20million%20to%20%2410%20million%20in%20under%20a%20year.%20Wordsmith%20also%20competes%20with%20a%20wave%20of%20startups%20attacking%20a%20smaller%20slice%20of%20work%20%E2%80%94%20contracts%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Spellbook%2C%20Ivo%2C%20and%20SimpleDocs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22839db16c-7588-4a98-8565-1e93ac3d3f0d%5C%22%3EIs%20Anthropic%20a%20friend%20or%20foe%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20%241%20trillion%20question%20hovering%20over%20every%20legal%20tech%20startup.%20What%20happens%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-submits-s-1-joins-ipo-race-with-openai-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20from%20behind%20and%20sweeps%20the%20market%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20rolled%20out%20dozens%20of%20agents%20that%20can%20perform%20one-off%20legal%20tasks%2C%20from%20reading%20contracts%20to%20writing%20policies%2C%20and%20says%20its%20agents%20can%20work%20across%20many%20of%20the%20software%20programs%20lawyers%20already%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20expansion%20has%20raised%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20legal%20teams%20need%20specialized%20legal%20software%20at%20all%20once%20their%20companies%20have%20deployed%20a%20general-purpose%20assistant%20across%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcNairn%20argues%20that%20Anthropic's%20push%20into%20legal%20is%20good%20for%20business.%20Tools%20like%20Claude%2C%20he%20said%2C%20give%20legal%20teams%20a%20taste%20of%20what%20artificial%20intelligence%20can%20do.%20Lawyers%20also%20learn%20the%20limits%20of%20using%20a%20broad-use%20platform%20to%20run%20a%20legal%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20analogy%20is%20that%20sales%20teams%20do%20not%20abandon%20Salesforce%20because%20they%20have%20Claude%2C%20and%20finance%20teams%20do%20not%20drop%20their%20accounting%20systems%20because%20they%20have%20a%20chatbot.%20Legal%20teams%2C%20he%20said%2C%20still%20need%20a%20system%20that%20can%20route%20work%2C%20manage%20permissions%2C%20enforce%20playbooks%2C%20keep%20records%2C%20and%20show%20how%20decisions%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaude's%20good%20for%20individuals%20doing%20individual%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20McNairn%20said.%20%26quot%3BWordsmith%20runs%20the%20function.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwordsmith-ai-for-corporate-lawyers-70-million-series-b-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780479001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1f1a5d2ab5f9757add81d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwordsmith-ai-for-corporate-lawyers-70-million-series-b-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wordsmith%2C%20a%20startup%20building%20AI%20software%20for%20corporate%20legal%20teams%2C%20has%20raised%20%2470%20million%20in%20funding%20from%20Index%20Ventures%20and%20other%20backers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Set%20602%20Business%20Goals%20In%20