s%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T213822.115_11zon-1756742924-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20fresh%20air%2C%20natural%20beauty%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20adventure%2C%20Karnala%20makes%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20a%20relaxed%20family%20getaway%3B%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40hegdevikhyat%2Fkarnala-fort-trek-914198736bbe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPicture%20source%3A%20Medium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20Panvel%2C%20check%20into%20a%20budget-friendly%20lodge%20or%20hotel.%20Good%20options%20near%20the%20station%20offer%20family%20rooms%20for%20around%20Rs%20800%20to%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20night%2C%20with%20basic%20amenities%20like%20clean%20beds%2C%20attached%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20Wi-Fi.%20Some%20hotels%20may%20offer%20early%20check-in%20if%20requested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUse%20the%20day%20to%20relax%20after%20travel.%20Visit%20Panvel%20Market%2C%20known%20for%20its%20bustling%20vegetable%20stalls%2C%20fruit%20vendors%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F423575%2Fmumbai-snack-seller-mansukh-dada-farsan-seller-borivali-west-jain-derasar-determination%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20snack%20shops%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dinner%20can%20be%20kept%20affordable%20with%20simple%20Maharashtrian%20thalis%20or%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Emisal%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epuri%20bhaji%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20local%20eateries%2C%20all%20within%20Rs%2060%20to%20Rs%20100%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%202%3A%20Exploring%20Karnala%20Bird%20Sanctuary%20%E2%80%93%20Birds%20and%20forest%20trails%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20breakfast%2C%20take%20a%20rickshaw%20or%20a%20state%20transport%20bus%20to%20Karnala%20Bird%20Sanctuary%2C%20located%20about%2013%20km%20from%20Panvel.%20A%20rickshaw%20costs%20around%20Rs%20250%20one%20way%2C%20while%20a%20bus%20or%20shared%20rickshaw%20will%20cost%20under%20Rs%2030%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntry%20to%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2060%20for%20adults%20and%20Rs%2030%20for%20children.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20small%20refundable%20deposit%20for%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20as%20the%20park%20strictly%20enforces%20a%20no-plastic%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpend%20the%20day%20walking%20through%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20shaded%20trails.%20Home%20to%20over%20150%20species%20of%20resident%20and%20migratory%20birds%2C%20including%20the%20Malabar%20grey%20hornbill%2C%20golden%20oriole%2C%20and%20paradise%20flycatcher%2C%20it%20is%20a%20place%20for%20nature%20lovers.%20Benches%20are%20placed%20along%20the%20paths%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F413732%2Fkoynanagar-young-guides-are-reviving-tourism-and-creating-jobs-homestays%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eideal%20for%20resting%20and%20birdwatching%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Karnala%20Fort%20trail%20begins%20inside%20the%20sanctuary%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mumbai%20Pune%20Adventures%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T214237.289_11zon-1756743171.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-