ate.%20The%20relentless%20heavy%20rains%20are%20compounded%20by%20the%20dangerously%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20Sutlej%2C%20Beas%2C%20and%20Ravi%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20drowning.%20It%20needs%20your%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonate%20to%20help%20Punjab%20flood%20victims%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%2C%20like%20the%203%2C54%2C000%20people%20(as%20of%205%20September)%20affected%2C%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20grieve.%20His%20only%20priority%20was%20ensuring%20that%20his%20family%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20house%20alive.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20escape%3B%20the%20only%20option%20was%20to%20wait%20and%20pray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496899%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20they%20saw%20a%20boat%20making%20its%20way%20to%20them.%20In%20it%20was%20Simranjit%20Singh%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Akal%20Relief%20Team%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391684%2Fcol-dr-rajinder-singh-started-akal-drug-de-addiction-centre-pu