d%20trade%20them%20away.%20Instead%2C%20he%20came%20home%20asking%20if%20I%20could%20pack%20more%20the%20next%20day.%20It%E2%80%99s%20become%20his%20go-to%20snack%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ritu%20Sharma%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20slowly%20started%20experimenting%20with%20other%20changes.%20A%20sprinkle%20of%20home-grown%20microgreens%20on%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Erotis%3C%2Fem%3E%20seemed%20like%20nothing%20at%20first%2C%20but%20over%20time%20he%20began%20noticing%20the%20extra%20crunch.%20These%20days%2C%20he%20even%20reminds%20me%20if%20I%20forget%20to%20add%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20little%20victories%20like%20this%20that%20make%20me%20feel%20reassured%20that%20he%E2%80%99s%20getting%20the%20right%20nutrition%20without%20the%20mealtime%20battles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20working%20parents%2C%20time%20is%20a%20real%20hurdle.%20But%20Sandhya%20reassures%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20now%20brands%20offering%20ready-to-make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336832%2Fias-officer-sushant-gaurav-transforms-gumla-district-of-jharkhand-with-ragi-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillet%20pancake%20mixes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20flours.%20Just%20add%20milk%20and%20cook.%20But%20always%20check%20the%20labels.%20Choose%20products%20with%20minimal%20preservatives%20and%20zero%20palm%20oil.%20And%20above%20all%2C%20pre-plan.%20Weekly%20meal%20prep%20makes%20life%20easier.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20not%20packaged%20foods%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%20are%20cautious%20about%20heavily%20marketed%20%E2%80%9Cnutrition%20drinks%E2%80%9D%20and%20packaged%20baby%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20nutritionist%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20recommend%20packaged%20milk-based%20food%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandhya%20says%20firmly.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20be%20used%20occasionally%2C%20but%20a%20simple%20homemade%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20porridge%20takes%20just%20five%20minutes%20and%20is%20far%20healthier.%20Parents%20underestimate%20how%20easy%20traditional%20options%20can%20be.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20agrees%2C%20warning%20against%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20bars%E2%80%9D%20and%20gummies%20with%20hidden%20sugars.%20%E2%80%9CCheck%20the%20labels.%20Less%20than%20four%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%2C%20at%20least%20four%20grams%20of%20protein%2C%20and%20no%20strange%20codes%20like%20E422%20or%20INS%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20checklist.%20Once%20parents%20learn%20to%20read%20labels%2C%20half%20the%20battle%20is%20won.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESigns%20that%20the%20nutrition%20plan%20is%20working%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20children%20eat%20better%2C%20the%20results%20go%20beyond%20physical%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201368px)%20100vw%2C%201368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%201368w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy